room_title: Escape room "Rocket Science" by Escape Cocoa Beach in Melbourne
room_address: 5675 N Atlantic Ave Unit 113/114 Cocoa Beach, FL 32931
room_description: You and your family are touring an aerospace facility. You wander off and find yourselves in the office of a scientist who mysteriously vanished in the 1960’s. He was studying extraterrestrial life, supernovas, and intergalactic travel. His office remains untouched. You have one hour to uncover the secret of his disappearance…
